<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-18-1029 </DOCNO><TEXT>The electric dipole polarizability of {sup 7}Li is studied theoretically.A consistent interpretation is obtained among the electric dipole polarizability,the quadrupole moment, the tensor analyzing powers for aligned {sup 7}Liscattering at sub-Coulomb energies, and the radiative capture (or photodis-integration) cross section for the {sup 3}H+{alpha}{yields} {sup 7}Li+{gamma}reaction.</TEXT></DOC>